s how this place works, majority of the ingredients is grown there on the spot. There are vineyards, gardens, lake side. Service is amazing and you feel happy there. I especially I want to mention Samuel the bar chef, who is an amazing person and told so much about the place and drinks.\nWe took ebikes to visit Locarno as well, which was great.\nI like the small details: how they gave us small presents, how flowers are changed every day, everything for us to feel care and importance.\nI will definitely come back.","time":"7 months ago"},{"author":"Fabian S.","rating":5,"text":"Amazing venue. Stefano from the beach bar is incredible. Today, he did a spontaneous mocktail workshop with 5 kids and everyone was absolutely excited. Thanks a lot for a wonderful day!","time":"5 months ago"},{"author":"Alma Teodora","rating":5,"text":"Super friendly, rural finca style luxury, discreetly located between vineyard with winery and golf course. Went for drinks & bruschetta at the private beach and loved the atmosphere of secluded paradise.","time":"6 months ago"}]'::jsonb,
