qqiDOaHBudzKTsxHIaCbp2t4bkku-RxGvkS9BA285w6Xnp9CE6KwIiGy7RdiXABqDtDyd6QC-Peug","width":600,"height":900,"attributions":["<a href=\"https://maps.google.com/maps/contrib/100073288897627773419\">Le Mas de La Rose</a>"]},{"photo_reference":"AcnlKN0PLrjLsWNq2ZQ6tDaRq6F_a-fivSrUSke3Z8OzzkMCdoNzjTW_kCvG7BrUSRYw0HsVISAy9VDAPPgmcL-t8NsFvoJnZEXPPP9k3IcObhgj3TKLB22biJ6omSfM_svKJw2jdz7kKKCLMsjC9MEzNb1ZBMshvDJYkVQoLGxqGf6c3Gnzhuka4N-MUIhHz5HSSwxcaxfoTufKJ5Zi2EDw8fEmQNHDB_7Kql3MEiktaUfHHJI_29FkNWEhckP559DryxLZdyrXdixGaPDCbJkKj4k0DLaMZiu49bhf_yzXB1aUqA","width":4800,"height":3201,"attributions":["<a href=\"https://maps.google.com/maps/contrib/100073288897627773419\">Le Mas de La Rose</a>"]}]'::jsonb, '[{"author":"Brooke Rosier","rating":5,"text":"We had the honor of having our wedding at Le Mas De La Rose. It was everything we could‚Äôve dreamed of and more. The setting is exquisite, the food is incredible, and the service is top notch. Above all, the staff makes the beautiful venue even more special. Veronique and Frank are so welcoming and fabulous. We are so grateful for the lovely experience we had and can‚Äôt wait to come back for a visit someday.","time":"3 months ago"},{"author":"Jed Weinstein","rating":5,"text":"We came here and couldn''t speak more highly of the property and the set-up.  Everything from the proximity to other cute towns, to the warm water in the pool, on-site hospitality and care, room being perfect to the food at the restaurant.  All-in-all, just an amazing 4.5 day trip to a beautiful part of Provence.","time":"3 months ago"},{"author":"Jessie Wiltshire","rating":5,"text":"My husband and I had the absolute privilege of getting married at Le Mas de la Rose in September 2025, and we can confidently say, it was an absolute dream come true.\n\nFrom the moment we first visited the venue 18 months before our big day, we knew this was somewhere truly unique. The estate itself is just breathtaking: from the beautifully designed rooms to the expansive grounds and the stunning swimming pool that looks straight out of a postcard. Every corner of Le Mas de la Rose feels like it was made for unforgettable moments.\n\nBut what truly sets this place apart is the incredible team, most especially Vero, who is the heart and soul of the experience. Vero is simply extraordinary. Despite managing so many weddings throughout the season, she made us feel like we were her only bride and groom. Her dedication, calm energy, incredible advice and meticulous attention to detail made our entire planning process seamless. During the wedding weekend itself, her warm presence gave us total peace of mind, allowing us to be genuinely relaxed and completely in the moment.\n\nThe venue layout is also ideal for a wedding: each part of the day flows naturally into the next, with separate yet connected spaces for the ceremony, cocktail hour, dinner, and dancing. The ambiance in the evening is just magical. And if you''re planning a second-day celebration, the pool bar area is so much fun!!\n\nOur guests were blown away, not only by the breathtaking setting, but also by the exceptional food and service. The catering was out of this world, and every single team member was polite, professional, and warm.\n\nWe can‚Äôt thank Vero and the entire team at Le Mas de la Rose enough for giving us a wedding weekend that exceeded our wildest dreams. If you''re considering this venue, do not hesitate. It is pure perfection. We are already so excited to come back and stay there soon! Xx","time":"3 months ago"},{"author":"Koralie","rating":5,"text":"I got married at Le Mas de la Rose in spring 2024, and honestly, it was everything I could have dreamed of. The venue is stunning, with endless olive trees, fields of lavender, a little vegetable garden, and even a tennis court. From the minute you arrive, you feel like you‚Äôve stepped into a different world.\n\nWe spent the whole weekend there, and I can truly say that our guests and I will never forget how incredible all the people were. The team at Le Mas de la Rose don‚Äôt just keep the place running, they make it shine even brighter. Every single person was warm, helpful, and genuinely kind. They made us feel so cared for, and their thoughtfulness made the celebration feel extra special.\n\nWhen it comes to weddings, V√©ronique is truly one of a kind. She is the heart of the place, and her energy sets the tone for everything. Her smile lifts everyone‚Äôs spirits, and she has this calm, reassuring presence that makes you feel instantly at ease. She pays attention to every detail and always has a solution, no matter how complicated the situation. I‚Äôll be honest: I was a rather demanding bride with a few wild requests. But not once did anyone say no to me. Instead, they listened and took the time to understand what I really needed. They always found a way to meet me in the middle, with solutions that made me feel supported and understood. Thanks to them, I was able to relax and really enjoy my wedding day.\n\nThe rest of the team was just as wonderful. Every staff member made sure my husband, our guests, and I were happy and comfortable the whole weekend. The weather was unpredictable, with strong winds and a bit of rain at times, but the staff had plans for every possibility, so everything went smoothly.\n\nThe restaurant at Le Mas de la Rose is also fantastic. The food was delicious, the desserts were a highlight, and the service was always warm and professional.\n\nWould I recommend Le Mas de la Rose? Absolutely. Our wedding was so special that I honestly wish I could do it all over again every year. If you‚Äôre looking for a magical place to get married in Provence, this is the one.","time":"7 months ago"},{"author":"Corin Muresan","rating":5,"text":"Such an incredible place!\nEverything is outstanding,  professional staff, amazing food, the service!\nJust amazing!","time":"4 months ago"}]'::jsonb,
