ul.\n\nThe restaurant was beautiful and the food was to a very high standard. Also lovely grounds and the winery over the road was a great experience. Highly recommend.","time":"a month ago"},{"author":"David Hoag","rating":5,"text":"I cannot say enough about the service and the level of hospitality and friendliness of the staff -- it was excellent and truly contributed to a very positive overall experience. The property is beuatiful, giving a feeling a luxury while being natural and in line with the environment and surroundings. Attention to detail was fantastic -- clean, well-appointed and decorated, comfortable, and the grounds and gardens are truly remarkable. Very relaxing and a welcome respite from being out and about. The meals were excellent -- dinner once, breakfast twice -- the breakfast was wonderful in terms of its choices for locally made/grown/sources products and fresh, delicious breads, meats, fruit, etc. Overall a wonderful experience, and worthy of its billing.","time":"2 months ago"},{"author":"Julia Hanauer","rating":5,"text":"One of the best hotels I''ve ever stayed at. Beautiful property, great location, and excellent service. Carine was particularly helpful and kind during our stay. My husband and I were able to totally relax here and enjoy the peace and quiet. Can''t recommend this property enough!","time":"3 months ago"},{"author":"Leonidas D.","rating":2,"text":"Is a typical hotel restaurant food thats lack in taste and creativity. Just safe options that you will eat but would never want to eat again. Dessert is ready made and the waiter just put it in a plate for you. Could be a really nice place but honestly what i can call it is just boring.","time":"2 months ago"},{"author":"PirateOfAvalon","rating":5,"text":"A beautiful hotel in a most traditional Provencal way. Set in a peaceful, luxurious, traditional environment, one could say it is a quiet Provence themed sanctuary, with attentive, helpful, and kind staff. The building, rooms and grounds exude traditional luxury and beauty without being ostentatious. You feel good upon arriving, and you sleep well.\nIf I had one complaint it is the restaurant, which does indeed serve very good food, but has a bit of a limited menu. The times I stayed were always off season so it may be different in the high season.\nI have stayed here more than once, and I look forward to returning.","time":"2 months ago"}]'::jsonb,
