taurants for dinner so we can explore the surrounding towns. The restaurant at this hotel is an Exception! It was THE BEST DINNER during our 2 week trip to France.\nSome of our favorites were soaking in the magnificent view from our balconies, the amazing breakfast on the outdoor terrace, and the dreamy jacuzzi by the spa.\nThank you, Chateau Saint-Martin, for your wonderful hospitality during our stay.","time":"5 months ago"},{"author":"Arthur Sevenet","rating":5,"text":"‚≠êÔ∏è‚≠êÔ∏è‚≠êÔ∏è‚≠êÔ∏è‚≠êÔ∏è A Truly Exceptional Stay ‚Äì The Best in the South of France\n\nOur recent stay at Ch√¢teau Saint-Martin was nothing short of outstanding. Beyond the breathtaking setting and elegant charm of the property ‚Äî which, in my opinion, is the finest venue in the South of France ‚Äî what truly elevates the experience is the incredible team.\n\nEvery member of the staff went above and beyond, combining warmth, professionalism, and a remarkable attention to detail that made us feel genuinely cared for throughout our stay. From the room touches to the thoughtful service at every turn, everything was perfectly executed.\n\nIt was an amazing experience from start to finish, and we‚Äôre already looking forward to returning. Bravo to the entire team ‚Äî you‚Äôve created something truly special.","time":"7 months ago"},{"author":"Michael Gross","rating":5,"text":"By far the best hotel we have ever stayed.  Having given other facilities 5 stars no room to upgrade this truly remarkable establishment. From first moment to last, utter perfection. No point in dissecting every facet, because no element fell below  the ultimate in professional care, quality and skill.","time":"5 months ago"},{"author":"ruwka","rating":5,"text":"We stayed here as a couple for 4 nights and absolutely loved everything. The service was outstanding, the staff were incredibly friendly and helpful, and the room was spotless and very comfortable.\n\nThe food was delicious ‚Äî beautifully presented and full of flavor, with very attentive service. The entire hotel is well-maintained, peaceful, and has all the amenities you need for a relaxing stay.\n\nWe didn‚Äôt try the spa or massage services, and honestly regret not doing so ‚Äî they looked amazing.\n\nExcellent value for money. One of the best hotel experiences we''ve had in years. Huge thanks to the entire hotel team for their amazing work ‚Äî we truly appreciated it. Highly recommended!","time":"7 months ago"}]'::jsonb,
