ony and then the actual wedding in the garden. The finishing touches included- harp music, horse drawn carriage rides while the wedding party took pictures, candlelight dinner, wedding dances outside, and the pi√®ce de r√©sistance- the fireworks. Thank you Cynthia, Teal and team for such a memorable weekend!!","time":"2 months ago"},{"author":"Kelly Ashton","rating":5,"text":"This will be a family vacation that will never be topped! We stayed at the Chateau last week and had the most fantastic experience. The staff was warm and welcoming. They catered to our every need. We had delicious meals prepared by their in house chef and they blew my mind every time! Cynthia planned a different experience each day we were there and they just exceeded all my expectations. I can‚Äôt wait to return one day for another fairytale adventure.","time":"4 months ago"},{"author":"Odris Chalas","rating":5,"text":"Ch√¢teau Chalain La Pottery feels like a dream gently brought to life. Mornings began with sunlight spilling through tall windows, and evenings ended with the soft hush of the gardens below. The ch√¢teau‚Äôs charm lies not only in its exquisite design but in the warmth of its hosts, who make every guest feel like a cherished friend. It is a place where time slows and elegance lingers ‚Äî a rare treasure to return to again and again.","time":"3 months ago"},{"author":"Ben Blanc","rating":5,"text":"Challain Castle is one of those wonderful French castles where newlyweds'' dreams can come true.\nAs a destination wedding photographer, I had the pleasure of spending several days there photographing the wedding of a couple who had traveled from afar, and it was a real pleasure to see the premium quality of service provided by the ch√¢teau staff and the owner to the bride and groom, of course, but also to my team and the various service providers.","time":"a month ago"},{"author":"Olga Tregubova","rating":5,"text":"May be my favorite place on earth. Love the careful, tasteful renovations, extraordinary hospitality, spectacular event planning.\n\nAnd to speak on how straightforward the owner/wedding planner is: our wedding was originally planned during peak pandemic, and I was able to reschedule with a text message. Our wedding ended up being ‚Äúthe best wedding we have ever been to‚Äù for all of our guests, and they have been to some world-class events.","time":"a year ago"}]'::jsonb,
