r a wedding - staff were very pleasant and food was very nice.","time":"4 months ago"},{"author":"Kelly Loft","rating":5,"text":"Our absolute dream wedding venue, everything was fantastic. Anna is simply incredible and her floristry skills are second to none. The grazing table on Friday went down so well and did Ed‚Äôs fabulous BBQ on the Sunday. Our wedding day ran like clockwork and the food was delicious. The chateau and its rooms are absolutely stunning and it was so lovely to have most of our guests stay with us. Erik was a fantastic host and took care of everyone amazingly. We had the BEST time and memories to last a lifetime. We simply couldn‚Äôt have asked for anything more. 5*","time":"a year ago"},{"author":"Tracey Williams","rating":5,"text":"Just arrived home after the most amazing, memorable, emotional wedding at Chateau Lagorce. We celebrated my daughter''s wedding to her childhood sweetheart and it was like a fairytale. Having a whole Chateau to share with friends and family for a long weekend was unreal. Anna and Ed have put their heart and soul into this Chateau keeping everything authentic. The kitchen was well equipped and the huge fridges meant we could stock up for the weekend. The wedding day was the best and the french celebrant was lovely . Anna''s flowers were so beautiful and the food/table setting etc was stunning. Evening Fireworks were wonderful and a must. Just want to say a huge thanks to Erik who looked after us all over the weekend, he never stopped. Best weekend I have ever had thanks so much Anna, Ed and Erik ‚ù§Ô∏è","time":"a year ago"},{"author":"Beth W","rating":5,"text":"We have just had our wedding at Chateau Lagorce. The whole weekend was magical, from grazing board welcome party on the Friday to the wedding and incredible bbq on Sunday. All of our guests were in awe of the venue and had the most spectacular weekend. Anna and Ed are the hosts with the most and Erik looked after the guests so well. If you can afford to do so,  definitely book Chateau Lagorce for your wedding and you won''t regret it. Thank you so so much for making our fairytale wedding a reality! ü•∞","time":"3 months ago"},{"author":"Patrick Murphy","rating":5,"text":"Attended our dear friends Son ''s wedding at le Chateau Lagorce and were regally treated by a most impressive and welcoming staff and owners Ed and Anna and all their colleagues especially Fred and his wife Myriam. Beautiful setting and beautiful service giving us beautiful memories","time":"a year ago"}]'::jsonb,
