ot recommend this place enough for a wedding! Oh, and the rooms!!! So dreamy and picturesque! Every detail is really thought out. 10/10 ü§©","time":"2 months ago"},{"author":"Eduardo Benito","rating":5,"text":"Stunning location, beautiful and individually styled rooms, made the wedding truly magical. The staff were so friendly and helpful. The quality and variety of food was superb throughout our 3 night stay. It''s an exceptional space, I cannot recommend this highly enough.","time":"4 months ago"},{"author":"Isabelle Gallagher","rating":5,"text":"This is truly a beautiful wedding venue. The whole place has so much charm, the rooms are gorgeous, and the atmosphere just feels incredibly welcoming. It‚Äôs the perfect setting for a wedding weekend, and the team is genuinely kind, attentive, and helpful from start to finish. I honestly couldn‚Äôt recommend it more","time":"a month ago"},{"author":"Jason Bean","rating":5,"text":"Ch√¢teau de la Couronne is an exceptional wedding venue and easily the most impressive I have ever visited. The quality and attention to detail throughout the ch√¢teau are outstanding, both indoors and across the beautiful grounds.\n\nWe visited in summer and were fortunate to experience fantastic weather, which highlighted just how perfect this venue is for a wedding celebration. The staff were professional, attentive, and incredibly welcoming throughout the entire weekend. Every element, from the ceremony and wedding meal to the evening BBQ was executed perfectly. I would highly recommend arranging a visit if you‚Äôre considering this venue. Thank you to the wonderful team at Ch√¢teau de la Couronne ü§©","time":"a week ago"},{"author":"Conway Wedding","rating":5,"text":"We got married at Ch√¢teau de la Couronne on August 2nd and had the most magical weekend of our lives. From the moment we had our first viewing, we were blown away- not just by how breathtaking the ch√¢teau is (and it is stunning), but by the warmth and care shown to us by Lucy, Charlie, and Ben. Leading up to the wedding and the weekend itself, they went above and beyond to make sure every detail was perfect and that we and our guests were looked after every step of the way.\n\nThe chateau food deserves its own review-it was absolutely phenomenal. Our guests still talk about it! From the incredible personalised Indian feast on Friday to the gorgeous breakfast spread each morning, and an absolute feast all day on Sunday, every meal was memorable. A small but meaningful touch I‚Äôll never forget: preparing me a plate of fresh watermelon while I was getting ready on the wedding day!\n\nThe work the team has done on the ch√¢teau is extraordinary. It''s elegant, stylish, full of character, and it provided the most beautiful, romantic backdrop for the wedding of our dreams. We truly had the best day of our lives and only wish we could relive it all over again.\n\nIf you‚Äôre even thinking about getting married here, do it. You won‚Äôt regret it.","time":"4 months ago"}]'::jsonb,
