and out! You want to get married here trust me- it‚Äôs a deal!","time":"4 years ago"},{"author":"T M","rating":1,"text":"The caretakers that live there are suppose to take care of the property however were extremely rude to our guests who needed their bedding changed. The chateau itself is filled with bugs and is not taken care of. The wedding planner associated with this venue lacks manners and basic etiquette. Her attitude contributed to a negative experience. Overall I found the staff associated with the venue to be horrendous.\n\nAs you can see from their reply they attempt to discredit saying they can‚Äôt find my details. The booking was made by my family and my name is withheld on google for privacy reasons. Rest assured our family and guests were disgusted by the lack of cleanliness, the appalling behaviour by the associated wedding planner and your drunk caretaker!","time":"3 weeks ago"},{"author":"Amber Lamphere (Amber Mae Photography)","rating":5,"text":"Ch√¢teau De Carsix is a magical location for your celebration or wedding. The stunning grounds and architecture of the ch√¢teau create the perfect fairytale ambiance. I loved photographing a September wedding here; it was one of the highlights of my photography career. This place is full of old-world charm and magic.","time":"2 years ago"},{"author":"Danielle Simmons","rating":5,"text":"I absolutely LOVED having my wedding at the Chateau de Carsix. The vendors they recommended were wonderful. The venue itself it gorgeous, clean, and warm. We hosted 47 people on the property for our wedding in April, and I wish we could do it all over again. It''s a magical space.","time":"6 years ago"},{"author":"Sarah","rating":5,"text":"My husband and I had a multi-day and multi-event wedding here back in June. It was the most magical venue that we could have imagines, and was able to accommodate all of our guests. Our wedding photos are now art all over our home. With the combination of this venue and Fabienne''s planning, we had the most amazing wedding.","time":"2 years ago"}]'::jsonb,
