en she sprung into a wonderful Irish accent and went about giving us a warm welcome. The Chateau sits just on the outskirts of Saumur and has plenty of shaded parking. The grounds of the residence are well kept with a good sized well maintained swimming pool at the back of the building. Our room was an exquisite suite with free standing tub and large shower in the bathroom with plenty of hot water. I could go on but there‚Äôs no need. It‚Äôs a 10/10 from us and we would definitely visit again.\nNick and Karen\nEssex uk üá¨üáß","time":"6 years ago"},{"author":"John Kraft","rating":5,"text":"The most gorgeous place we have ever stayed  with its tasteful French antique decor  yet homely atmosphere!  Divine ! Wonderful staff and  breakfast  and gardens!  Like a dream!  Mary Connor X Monique so warm x helpful.  Many thanks from Geraldine . Ann . Sue.  Helena . The Aussies","time":"7 years ago"},{"author":"Guillaume Nerzic","rating":4,"text":"Chateau de Beaulieu is a very comfortable and large house run by a very friendly and francophile Irish couple. The room we stayed in was great and we were able to enjoy the rest of the house and the garden (which features a swiming pool).","time":"5 years ago"}]'::jsonb,
